{
  "stem": "6736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Goeth went over, and he said, what is those?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What's going on here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So before the German could have said anything to him, he said a Jew is fighting with my-- with German-- how dare you?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said to her-- said to him, shoot her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he wouldn't shoot her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he gave another order.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he shot her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two of my friends put her in a wheelbarrow and brought her over to the-- there was a special place, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they throw her in the-- and by the way, whenever they took people from our barracks-- for no reason at all-- to the [NON-ENGLISH], the will always scream at us, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is remember, [NON-ENGLISH] is revenge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we heard that they had been shot, we run into the barracks and we started saying a prayer for them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because evenings was evening prayer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the best we could say for ourselves, that they are better off than we are.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For them at least we say a prayer, and they are finished with the misery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But for us, who's going to say a prayer for us?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's why to fulfill what they were asking of us, we couldn't take revenge.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish people do not take revenge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [NON-ENGLISH], we must remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why we have to fulfill the obligation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In '43, in August or September, a new administrator by the name of Frank was getting i a villa in Cracow to be the commander for whole Poland.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because Cracow was the hauptstadt, the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The capital.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wants to show him that he is help-- is working with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He asked us to load up two truckloads of topsoil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know or understand what it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
